PN,41821
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772010305
OL,3,CMeet Hugo, the first baby born in the
OL,4,CUK after womb transplant from dead
OL,5,Cdonor
OL,7,FTransplants from deceased donors only
OL,8,Fhappen when the families of those who
OL,9,Fhave died are asked specifically if
OL,10,Fthey wish to donate the womb.
OL,12,FThe womb is not covered by the normal
OL,13,Fconsent for donation, nor by joining
OL,14,Fthe organ donor register, and it is
OL,15,Fnot covered by deemed consent (which
OL,16,Fpresumes people want to donate unless
OL,17,Fthey opt out).
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G21/24
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
