CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772010305
OL,3,CMeet Hugo, the first baby born in the
OL,4,CUK after womb transplant from dead
OL,5,Cdonor
OL,7,F"We are very grateful to any families
OL,8,Fwho choose to give the additional
OL,9,Fconsent for donation to this
OL,10,Fprogramme."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G24/24
